" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfb6a5b0439f9f9b4963b5c5fe868100394c1c6","tid":1522031,"uid":163753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e816c98771a4f55397cd828900277439554a62","tid":1522031,"uid":292497,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"唉頂開左咁大火做乜唔走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212e3d1d6f66e7da464764cbfa28fcba35125756","tid":1522031,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed3e0c247192e86aaae68e4cdd2467fa642e3d6b","tid":1522031,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"屌捉左一男一女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"鳩行定係勇武?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6621c20cd14afd8f50f8807a73fe1b0bd384941","tid":1522031,"uid":139282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液+薑，開水沖，唔傷皮膚"},{"pid":"cb76da90661c936d015539789a90218166e62bde","tid":1522031,"uid":314979,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqXNToX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqXNToX.gif&h=77aac523&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05881e7d157637fd5ab6dbe02eb918c6bcb42640","tid":1522031,"uid":80763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"打死都唔割"},{"pid":"77b24a25315a571f86cde1d7600b7d50c487953c","tid":1522031,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212e3d1d6f66e7da464764cbfa28fcba35125756","tid":1522031,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed3e0c247192e86aaae68e4cdd2467fa642e3d6b","tid":1522031,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"屌捉左一男一女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"鳩行定係勇武?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"有FULL GEAR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389a850a96ce73db1fd3a3e8e5e87b9c7848a7da","tid":1522031,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4a8916d834be2d1d1e1d1817361fc7662737d7